msgctxt "sn42.13:32.1"
msgid "Evaṃ vutte, pāṭaliyo gāmaṇi bhagavantaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr "When he said this, Pāṭaḷiya the chief said to the Buddha:"

msgctxt "sn42.13:32.2"
msgid "“abhikkantaṃ, bhante, abhikkantaṃ, bhante … pe …"
msgstr "“Excellent, sir! Excellent! …"

msgctxt "sn42.13:32.3"
msgid "ajjatagge pāṇupetaṃ saraṇaṃ gatan”ti."
msgstr ""
"From this day forth, may Master Gotama remember me as a lay follower who has "
"gone for refuge for life.”"

